# 🚀 JavaScript Mini Projects

A curated collection of mini projects made using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. 
Each project is simple, clean, and designed for learning or showcasing front-end fundamentals.

## 🛠 How to Use

You don’t need any fancy setup!  
Just clone the repository and open the HTML file in your browser.

### 🔽 Clone this repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Akshatf/mini-projects.git
```
```
cd mini-projects
```
▶️ Run a Project
Go to any project folder and open the index.html file:

🛠 Tech Stack
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript

🙌 Support & Feedback
If you like these projects, feel free to ⭐ star the repository and share feedback or suggestions via issues.

